paragraphs.text:
run("
SELECT *
FROM(
    SELECT orderDate
            ,COUNT(DISTINCT atb.subOrderId) AS suborders
            ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (shippedStatus <> 'CLD' OR shippedStatus IS NULL OR shippedStatus = 'NA') THEN atb.subOrderId ELSE NULL END) AS shipped_suborder
            ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN deliveredDate is not null then atb.subOrderId else null end) as delivered_suborder
            ,SUM(NMIncAd)/COUNT(DISTINCT atb.subOrderId) AS NMBO
            ,round((count(distinct case when shippedStatus='RTO' and rtoDate is not null then atb.subOrderId end))/(COUNT(DISTINCT atb.subOrderId)) * 100,2) as rto_percent
            ,round((COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (shippedStatus <> 'CLD' OR shippedStatus IS NULL OR shippedStatus = 'NA') THEN atb.subOrderId ELSE NULL END))/(COUNT(DISTINCT atb.subOrderId)) * 100,2) as shipped_percent
            ,round((COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN deliveredDate is not null then atb.subOrderId else null end))/(COUNT(DISTINCT atb.subOrderId)) * 100,2) as delivered_percent
    FROM(
        SELECT *       
        FROM `temp.order_sd_2`
        WHERE orderDate>'2023-03-15'
            AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%capi%'
            AND LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%fb%'
        ) atb
    
    LEFT JOIN(
            SELECT DISTINCT subOrderId
                            ,shippedStatus
                            ,deliveredDate
                            ,rtoDate
            FROM `all(agCmDump)`
            ) ag
    ON atb.subOrderId = ag.subOrderId
    
    LEFT JOIN(
            SELECT DISTINCT subOrderId
                            ,NMIncAd
            FROM `all(unitEconomicsBaseTable)`
            ) ue
    ON atb.subOrderId = ue.subOrderId
    
    GROUP BY orderDate
    ORDER BY orderDate
    )
",1000)
